+-----------------+-------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------+
| Class           | Responsibilities                                |	Collaborators               |
+-----------------+-------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------+
| User	          | Register for event	                            | Event, LotteryManager       |
|                 | Check lottery status	                          | LotteryManager              |
|-----------------+-------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------+
| Event	          | Store event details	User                        | User, LotteryManager        |
|                 | Manage participant list	                        | LotteryManager              |
|-----------------+-------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------+
| LotteryManager  |	Assign users to events based on lottery results | User, Event                 |
|                 | Notify users of lottery results	                | User                        |
|-----------------+-------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------+
| Admin	          | Maintain platform	                              | User, Event, LotteryManager |
|-----------------+-------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------+